dct_title_s: Map showing the line of the Cairo & Fulton Railroad and its connections
dct_description_sm: Inset: Map of part of the United States and Mexico showing the north eastern & south western connections of the Cairo & Fulton R.R. (20 x 30 cm.). Relief shown by hachures. "Entered according to Act of Congress in the year 1871 by G.W. & C.B. Colton in the Office of the Librarian of Congress, at Washington."
dct_publisher_sm: New York : G.W. & C.B. Colton & Co., c1871.
